---

meta :
    author      : "DryKISS"
    description : "Footer, can provide organisation, social and location information - CodeBlender"
    image       : "Image"
    subject     : "DryKISS"
    title       : "Footer, can provide organisation, social and location information - CodeBlender"
    type        : "website"

heading :
    small : "Provides contextual information for the site"
    title : "Footer partial"

see :
    - - "Bootstrap Sticky Footer"
      - "http://getbootstrap.com/examples/sticky-footer/"

todo :
    - - "Enable the samples to be placed in a container-fluid"
    - - "Enable the footer to be fixed also - css"
